{"type": "article", "id": 28931, "title": "接线板", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-30T06:55:42Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 73, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703123705zSMeRlqBE9OZIQX5.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>你是不是曾因为接线板显得太突兀恨不得把它们藏起来？意大利初创公司 Woodie Milano 推出的 WoodieHub 希望能通过实用又美观的设计挑战人们对这种日常用品的刻板印象。WoodieHub 有混凝土、木质和大理石三种不同材质可供选择，全部由意大利工匠手工制作。时尚简洁的造型能够融入不同的环境当中，背面的纳米微吸胶可以使它牢固地贴在任何平面上。除了配有通用 AC 插座之外，WoodieHub 还提供了 USB 接口和无线充电功能，可以满足不同电子设备的需要。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/452242103/woodiehub-rethink-how-you-see-powerstrips\">链接</a>参与众筹，早鸟价为 89 欧元（混凝土版）。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123702QshOEfS5e791XKIP.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.60882353\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123703ANBfLSuYICWFdmrz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76426426\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123703MmKf7sgOvzW5b2et.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76444444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123704s2qhI3WFkOLfvKbT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54411765\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031237044COck9V3AetvRQHq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.52352941\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}